column6: - It's Kraven's Last Hunt in KILLVILLE...and Detectives Misty Knight and Paladin are the hunted! - Lord Sinister's secret weapon is his top shelf chef, MATT MURDOCK! But what happens when Sinister comes between Murdock and his love, rare food scout COLLEKTRA? - The BEST SECRET WARS ANTHOLOGY continues! YOU HEARD US, SECRET WARS: BATTLEWORLD!
column8: | penciller (cover):Sanford Greene | artist:Jonathan Marks | writer:Kevin Maurer | writer:Simon Spurrier
